				\begin{document}$$\mu$$\end{document}bar, at 210 mbar O2, with a light intensity of 1500 μ\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
